{
  "_README": [
    "Seed data for the JobRole, Industry, and Skill taxonomies.",
    "On every backend startup the seed runner UPSERTS these by `key` — so editing this file and restarting the backend updates names/families/aliases without losing existing IDs or candidate data.",
    "",
    "ROLE: { key, name, family, description? }",
    "  key      stable internal id (do not change once used)",
    "  name     display label",
    "  family   broad bucket — used for grouping in UI and for fuzzy match scoring",
    "",
    "INDUSTRY: { key, name }",
    "",
    "SKILL: { key, name, families[], aliases[] }",
    "  families[]   which role families this skill is relevant to (used for scoring)",
    "  aliases[]    alternate spellings/names so search and free-text matching catches them"
  ],

